[[File:Townhouse_256.png|right|256px]]
The '''Townhouse''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It enables taxation. Income from tax can be increased by connecting [[Marketplace]]s and [[Harbor]]s.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 5

